{"id": "samsung_elec-2026-05-14-010", "date": "2026-05-14", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 5, "week": 20, "weekday": "Thu"}, "entities": {"companies": ["samsung_elec"], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": [], "sentiment": {"label": "neutral", "score": 0.0, "keywords": []}, "importance": {"score": 0.5, "reasons": []}, "title": "Samsung Launches Samsung AI Week 2026 for AI-Powered Living", "content": "Samsung Electronics is hosting Samsung AI Week 2026 from May 11 to June 7 in 58 countries. Now in its seventh year, Samsung Week has become the company’s largest annual global promotion, celebrating its founding anniversary and thanking customers for their continued support with exclusive deals on a wide range of products. Beginning this year, […]", "sources": [{"name": "samsung_elec", "url": "https://news.samsung.com/global/samsung-launches-samsung-ai-week-2026-for-ai-powered-living", "type": "rss"}]}
{"id": "samsung_elec-2026-05-14-011", "date": "2026-05-14", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 5, "week": 20, "weekday": "Thu"}, "entities": {"companies": ["samsung_elec"], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": [], "sentiment": {"label": "neutral", "score": 0.0, "keywords": []}, "importance": {"score": 0.5, "reasons": []}, "title": "Samsung Adopts New EU Code of Conduct for Energy Smart Appliances", "content": "Samsung Electronics today announced that it has signed the European Union’s (EU) Code of Conduct (CoC) for interoperability and Energy Smart Appliances (ESAs). The CoC aims to accelerate the rollout of connected appliances that can work seamlessly with energy systems and help households use electricity more efficiently. “Samsung believes connected appliances can play a meaningful […]", "sources": [{"name": "samsung_elec", "url": "https://news.samsung.com/global/samsung-adopts-new-eu-code-of-conduct-for-energy-smart-appliances", "type": "rss"}]}
{"id": "tcl-2026-05-14-012", "date": "2026-05-14", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 5, "week": 20, "weekday": "Thu"}, "entities": {"companies": ["tcl", "csot", "samsung_elec", "boe"], "customers": ["tcl", "samsung_elec"], "suppliers": ["csot", "boe"]}, "topics": ["oled_penetration"], "sentiment": {"label": "neutral", "score": 0.0, "keywords": []}, "importance": {"score": 0.9, "reasons": ["多公司提及", "供應鏈上下游同時提及"]}, "title": "Will Samsung utilize AMOLEDs produced by BOE for its Galaxy S27 phone basic model?", "content": "<p>A couple of months ago we reported that Samsung Electronics, aiming to reduce its cost structure, has <a href=\"https://www.oled-info.com/samsung-electronics-orders-15-million-oled-panels-tcl-csot-its-2026-a5-and-fe\">ordered 15 million AMOLED panels from CSOT</a>, that are adopted in the 2026 Galaxy A57 and S FE models smartphones.</p><div class=\"align-center\">\n  \n  <a href=\"https://www.oled-info.com/sites/default/files/2025-01/Samsung-Galaxy-S25.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">\n    \n    <img loading=\"la", "sources": [{"name": "oled_info", "url": "https://www.oled-info.com/will-samsung-utilize-amoleds-produced-boe-its-galaxy-s27-phone-basic-model", "type": "rss"}]}
{"id": "boe-2026-05-14-013", "date": "2026-05-14", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 5, "week": 20, "weekday": "Thu"}, "entities": {"companies": ["boe"], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": ["oled_penetration"], "sentiment": {"label": "positive", "score": 0.5, "keywords": ["mass production"]}, "importance": {"score": 0.5, "reasons": []}, "title": "BOE to start mass producing 14-inch laptop OLED panels at its 8.6-Gen OLED line in Chengdu by the end of the month", "content": "<p>BOE is accelerating its B16 8.6-Gen IT AMOLED fab in Chengdu, and according to the latest updates from Korea, the company will begin mass production by the end of this month (May 2026).</p><img src=\"https://www.oled-info.com/sites/default/files/inline-images/BOE-B16-Chengdu-8-6-gen-amoled-fab.jpg\" data-entity-uuid=\"71441b51-ce79-4bc0-9dd9-c737bc866d1c\" data-entity-type=\"file\" width=\"551\" height=\"301\" class=\"align-center\" loading=\"lazy\"><p>BOE's first products out of this new line will be 14-i", "sources": [{"name": "oled_info", "url": "https://www.oled-info.com/boe-start-mass-producing-14-inch-laptop-oled-panels-its-86-gen-oled-line", "type": "rss"}]}
