{"id": "unknown-2026-05-14-015", "date": "2026-05-14", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 5, "week": 20, "weekday": "Thu"}, "entities": {"companies": [], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": ["earnings"], "sentiment": {"label": "positive", "score": 1.0, "keywords": ["record"]}, "importance": {"score": 0.9, "reasons": ["涉及財報", "情緒極端"]}, "title": "Memory supply crunch pushes Phison to historic earnings", "content": "Phison Electronics posted record earnings in April as the artificial intelligence boom and tightening NAND flash supply drove memory prices sharply higher, underscoring the growing influence of AI demand across the semiconductor storage industry.", "sources": [{"name": "digitimes_display", "url": "https://www.digitimes.com/news/a20260514PD240/phison-earnings-demand-inventory-nand-flash.html", "type": "rss"}]}
{"id": "unknown-2026-05-14-016", "date": "2026-05-14", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 5, "week": 20, "weekday": "Thu"}, "entities": {"companies": [], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": ["earnings"], "sentiment": {"label": "positive", "score": 0.5, "keywords": ["growth"]}, "importance": {"score": 0.75, "reasons": ["涉及財報"]}, "title": "QBit Semiconductor targets edge AI growth as copier chips turn oligopolistic", "content": "IC design firm QBit Semiconductor will list on the Emerging Stock Board on May 15, 2026, and chairman Simon Shen, a former Kinpo executive, said the debut marks a new milestone for the company and underscores a promising growth outlook.", "sources": [{"name": "digitimes_display", "url": "https://www.digitimes.com/news/a20260514PD233/asic-ic-design-chips-growth.html", "type": "rss"}]}
{"id": "unknown-2026-05-14-017", "date": "2026-05-14", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 5, "week": 20, "weekday": "Thu"}, "entities": {"companies": [], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": ["earnings"], "sentiment": {"label": "positive", "score": 0.5, "keywords": ["growth"]}, "importance": {"score": 0.75, "reasons": ["涉及財報"]}, "title": "Tower Semiconductor secures US$1.3 billion in silicon photonics commitments as AI demand accelerates", "content": "Tower Semiconductor reported a strong start to 2026, marked by double-digit revenue growth and a significant jump in net profit. Following a \"solid\" first quarter, the company issued guidance for the second quarter that would represent the highest revenue in its history. Management highlighted surging growth in silicon photonics and a strategic restructuring of manufacturing in Japan as key drivers of long-term expansion.", "sources": [{"name": "digitimes_display", "url": "https://www.digitimes.com/news/a20260514VL206/tower-semiconductor-photonics-silicon-revenue-demand.html", "type": "rss"}]}
{"id": "unknown-2026-05-14-018", "date": "2026-05-14", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 5, "week": 20, "weekday": "Thu"}, "entities": {"companies": [], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": ["earnings"], "sentiment": {"label": "neutral", "score": 0.0, "keywords": []}, "importance": {"score": 0.75, "reasons": ["涉及財報"]}, "title": "Swancor taps aerospace, AI robots to lift revenue", "content": "Swancor Holding is continuing its push into high-value materials, with aerospace composites and AI robot-related businesses now accounting for 14% and 4% of revenue, respectively. Alongside these contributions, the company is targeting the AI server supply chain with its M8 copper-clad laminate (CCL) materials, which have already entered the customer testing phase, though shipment volumes currently remain low.", "sources": [{"name": "digitimes_display", "url": "https://www.digitimes.com/news/a20260513PD218/swancor-materials-revenue-2026-earnings.html", "type": "rss"}]}
{"id": "unknown-2026-05-14-019", "date": "2026-05-14", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 5, "week": 20, "weekday": "Thu"}, "entities": {"companies": [], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": ["it_panel_demand", "earnings"], "sentiment": {"label": "neutral", "score": 0.0, "keywords": []}, "importance": {"score": 0.75, "reasons": ["涉及財報"]}, "title": "Pegatron 1Q26 earnings fall more than 60% amid off-season, eyes stronger 2Q26 on AI PC demand", "content": "Pegatron announced its first-quarter 2026 financial results on May 13, with profit down more than 60% compared with the same period a year earlier, while earnings per share (EPS) hit its lowest level for the same period in nearly seven years.", "sources": [{"name": "digitimes_display", "url": "https://www.digitimes.com/news/a20260514PD200/pegatron-demand-2026-earnings-profit.html", "type": "rss"}]}
